data.description: Seller is offering $5,000.00 towards buyers closing cost, with a full priced offer. Come check out this newly updated home in Ocala Park Estates. This home is 1014 sq ft and has 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, with an oversized 1-car garage. The home features vaulted ceilings and tile flooring throughout, with laminate in the bedrooms. The home has lots of updates, new paint throughout, a brand new kitchen featuring new stainless steel appliances, new cabinets and granite countertops and both bathrooms have been updated. Outside there is a large storage shed and a 12 x 16 covered back porch. Roof was done is 2008 and the septic was pumped and inspected this year.  Schedule your showing today!
